# PLAYER::GET_PLAYER_HAS_RESERVE_PARACHUTE

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
This function returns true if player has a reserve parachute.
